title: Twenty One Pilots Drummer Takes to the Skies at Magic Kingdom Park
text:
While traveling to perform a concert in Tampa, Josh Dun of the band Twenty One Pilots, took a detour at Walt Disney World Resort for some Disney fun. He took a ride aboard Astro Orbiter in Tomorrowland to really take in the view of Magic Kingdom Park . 
Donâ€™t miss the rest of the Twenty One Pilots tour and get to a show before the tour wraps up in June!
Thanks to our fearless photographer, Chloe Rice.
